! 2005-07-08 - Gloria CORTI
 - Modified to use interface package Sim/GDML.
   Contains specialized GiGaRunAction to write a GDML file in Gauss containing 
   all geometry used in a job called "GDMLRunAction". 
   An example of the options necessary to activate it and to set properties
   in provided in options: GDMLWriter.opts
   Possible options are: 
   "Output" to set the name of the file to be written (default = "LHCb.gdml")
   "Schema" to set the GDML schema to be used

